ygData.messageBody:
Hello all... There is a new guild on the rise in
Drinal. Based out of Cabilis in the lands of Kunark, the
Ethereal Dragon Legion is looking for Dark Raced recruits.
If you wish to learn more about us and/or join
please refer all e-mail's to
Slixall@....<br><br>If you wish to join include the following
information:<br>Character's Name <br>Character's Race<br>Character
Class<br>Character's Bio<br>Character Screenshot(s)<br>Character's
Current Bind Point Location<br><br>After recieving this
information I will put it under review and give you an e-mail
of conformation on the following steps that need to
be taken.If you wish to contact me on other terms
you may on ICQ #107061572 (Slixall).<br><br>Thanks
for hearing me out and happy hunting.
